    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. Inspired by Thai 'chu chi' curry, this fragrant fish supper delivers tons of flavour. The whole family can enjoy its warming (but not too spicy!) heat and best of all, you just pop it in the oven!",
